entries.name: address
entries.desc: The host these services run on.

entries.name: bitmap
entries.desc: A bit map of enabled services on this host. If protocol is 6 (TCP) then the 26th bit corresponds to the SMTP service (port 25).  If this bit is set, then an SMTP server should be listening on TCP port 25; if zero, SMTP service is not supported.

entries.name: protocol
entries.desc: IP protocol number for these services.
